# brand-knowledge.md — Competitors and positioning

> Copy this file to `$HERMES_WORKSPACE/brand-knowledge.md` and fill it in with 5-10 competitors of your brand.
> Hermes reads this file for its Saturday-ideas proposals (product differentiation, niche opportunities).

